Package: geodesichange
Type: Package
Title: Change-Point Detection With Geodesic Distance
Version: 2024.4.15
Author: Toby Dylan Hocking
Maintainer: Toby Dylan Hocking <toby.hocking@r-project.org>
Description: Disk-based implementation of
 Functional Pruning Optimal Partitioning
 for change-point detection in angular data,
 using the geodesic distance,
 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geodesic>
 can handle huge data sets (10^7 or more).
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: Rcpp, data.table (>= 1.15.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests: testthat, ggplot2
URL: https://github.com/tdhock/geodesichange
BugReports: https://github.com/tdhock/geodesichange/issues
